---
// src/pages/projects/attendance-management-system.astro
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <div class="container py-8 mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="flex justify-center">
      <div class="w-full lg:w-10/12">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md overflow-hidden p-6">
          <!-- Project Title -->
          <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-blue-600 mb-6">Attendance Management System</h1>
          
          <!-- Technology Stack -->
          <div class="mb-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-2">Technology Stack</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700">ASP.NET, C#, HTML, CSS, Bootstrap, SQL Server</p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Project Overview -->
          <div class="mb-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-2">Project Overview</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              I developed a comprehensive Attendance Management System to automate the process of tracking, 
              managing, and reporting employee attendance. This system provides organizations with an 
              efficient solution for maintaining accurate attendance records, improving operational transparency.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Key Highlights -->
          <div class="mb-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-3">Key Highlights</h2>
            <ul class="space-y-4">
              <li>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">User Interface</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                  The system's front-end was designed using HTML, CSS, and Bootstrap, delivering a responsive 
                  and intuitive user interface. The design ensures compatibility across desktops, tablets, 
                  and smartphones, providing a seamless experience.
                </p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">Backend Development</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                  The backend was developed using ASP.NET and C#, ensuring a robust and scalable architecture.
                  The use of ASP.NET facilitated the integration of essential business logic, while C# enabled 
                  efficient handling of attendance tracking and reporting.
                </p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">Database</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                  The system employs SQL Server as the database, ensuring reliable and efficient data storage.
                </p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 text-gray-700 space-y-1">
                  <li>Employee records management</li>
                  <li>Attendance tracking with timestamps</li>
                  <li>Leave management system</li>
                  <li>Reporting and analytics</li>
                </ul>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Core Features -->
          <div class="mb-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-3">Core Features</h2>
            <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                <span class="ml-2 text-gray-700">User authentication with role-based access</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                <span class="ml-2 text-gray-700">Real-time attendance tracking</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                <span class="ml-2 text-gray-700">Leave management system</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                <span class="ml-2 text-gray-700">Automated reporting and analytics</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                <span class="ml-2 text-gray-700">Shift and overtime management</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                <span class="ml-2 text-gray-700">Biometric integration support</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Security Measures -->
          <div class="mb-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-3">Security Measures</h2>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5 9V7a5 5 0 0110 0v2a2 2 0 012 2v5a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-5a2 2 0 012-2zm8-2v2H7V7a3 3 0 016 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                <span class="ml-2 text-gray-700">
                  <strong>Role-Based Access Control:</strong> Implemented secure authentication and authorization mechanisms, 
                  restricting access to sensitive data and features based on user roles.
                </span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5 9V7a5 5 0 0110 0v2a2 2 0 012 2v5a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-5a2 2 0 012-2zm8-2v2H7V7a3 3 0 016 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                <span class="ml-2 text-gray-700">
                  <strong>Data Validation:</strong> Applied client-side and server-side validation to ensure 
                  the integrity of user input and prevent vulnerabilities like SQL injection.
                </span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5 9V7a5 5 0 0110 0v2a2 2 0 012 2v5a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-5a2 2 0 012-2zm8-2v2H7V7a3 3 0 016 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                <span class="ml-2 text-gray-700">
                  <strong>Encrypted Transactions:</strong> Secured sensitive data, including user credentials 
                  and attendance records, with encryption protocols.
                </span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Outcome -->
          <div class="mb-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-2">Outcome</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              The Attendance Management System significantly improved organizational efficiency by automating 
              attendance tracking, reducing manual errors, and providing real-time insights into employee 
              attendance patterns. Its intuitive interface and comprehensive reporting capabilities enabled 
              managers to make data-driven decisions about workforce management.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mt-2">
              This project demonstrates my expertise in developing enterprise-grade solutions using ASP.NET, 
              C#, and SQL Server, with a strong focus on usability, security, and scalability.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Back Button -->
          <div class="text-center">
            <a href="/myproject" class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 border border-blue-600 text-blue-600 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-600 hover:text-white transition-colors">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18" />
              </svg>
              Back to Projects
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>